{"type": "article", "id": 15024, "title": "倒三角锥玻璃花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-17T08:46:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004253fev07VAPYoOR9jtz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个玻璃花瓶源于荷兰设计师 Mart van Schijndel 在 1981 年推出的经典作品，多年之后，由他的女儿 Meike van Schijndel 重新推出。在荷兰完成手工制作，仅用三块玻璃片和硅胶，就能使花瓶呈现出倒立的三角锥的形状，同时保证站立，极有艺术感。售价 99 欧，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/glass-delta-vase/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142407XyvlKGH8JFnUQOko.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"1252\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33191489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142407AWUu9HTmbDFLvO4g.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"1173\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.24787234\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}